content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-16.

photos.alt: A photo of a landscape visible from a terrace: various trees in the foreground, a car bridge middle, and various houses and buildings with trees in-between further away. On the horizon it is possible to see the skyscrapers of the La Défense, just some high buildings, and a very faint silhouette of the Eiffel Tower, followed by a hill of Mont Valérien. The sky is covered with clouds.
